text: Tukkuguda is a municipality in Rangareddy district, Telangana, India. It falls under Maheswaram mandal. It is 27 kilometers away from Hyderabad. The Outer Ring Road, Hyderabad has a major junction passing through this village. Rajiv Gandhi International Airport is 7 kilometers away. The Ayyappa temple is located in the village. Around 5000 to 8000 people live here as per 2010 census. ==References== Category:Villages in Ranga Reddy district
title: Tukkuguda
